<h2 id="a-simpler-strumming-pattern">A simpler strumming patternâ€¦</h2>

<p>If you want something simpler to use while playing this song (intro, verse, etc)â€¦ just use this more straightforward pattern. Keep all chord changes on the â€œ1â€ count. This avoids complicated rhythms &amp; chord changes will make it much tougher to sing &amp; play at the same time.</p>

